item.title: Model help, not working
item.dc:creator: @badger41 badger41
item.description:
@badger41 wrote:

i know why he thought the .mdl is what he needed, i was helping him before and i said he needed a .mdl file so he could use a model that was from the 500+ rs cache.
to prevent further confusion let me clear things up.
the .mdl file is the original file out of the rscache, depending on what type of mode grabber you use
if you have a 500+ rscache model then your going to need the .mdl to use convert new2old in order to use it in the 317.
after youve converted it, i forget whether it has anim data still or not, but after youve converted it, you have to THEN make the .dat and gzip, make ints, etc.

it should work then.
